# Mobile Rules (Android/iOS)

## Purpose
Mobile app for map usage.

## Responsibilities
- Display map (MapLibre Native)
- Call backend API
- Handle mobile UX

## Data Access
- MUST call API
- MUST NOT connect to database

## Architecture
- Use clean architecture:
  UI → ViewModel → API Client

## Performance
- Optimize for low bandwidth
- Support offline tiles (PMTiles later)

## Rules
- Keep logic thin
- Reuse API endpoints
- Do not duplicate backend logic

## Future
- Add offline support
- Add routing